Ugh, I'm so hungry the room's starting to spin...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093205_MSG0020

Might as well stick it out, dammit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093205_MSG0040

Feel free to join in too, folks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093205_MSG0050
rows.name:
Oh? Join in what?
Is it something fun?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093205_MSG0060
rows.name:
Yeah, you can bet your bottom dollar.
Mind if I borrow your kitchen counters?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093205_MSG0070
rows.name: They should be arriving any minute now...[ST:wait ]
